88","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#placeholder-content","content":"Provide fallback SVG content while icons load from the CDN:"},"309":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-89","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#decorative-icons","content":"For purely decorative icons, no additional attributes are needed. The icon will have `role=\"presentation\"` and be ignored by screen readers:"},"310":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-90","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#semantic-icons","content":"For icons that convey meaning, use the `title` prop. This automatically adds `role=\"img\"` and provides screen reader accessible text:"},"311":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-91","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#interactive-icons","content":"For interactive icons within buttons or links, use the `title` prop on the icon and `aria-label` on the interactive element:"},"312":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-92","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-icon-loading","content":"Icons are loaded on-demand from a CDN using the following process:"},"313":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-93","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-icon-loading","content":"**First Request**: When an icon is first encountered, it triggers an asynchronous fetch from the CDN"},"314":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-94","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-icon-loading","content":"**SVG Parsing**: The fetched SVG string is parsed into a React element using `@bento/svg-parser`"},"315":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-95","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-icon-loading","content":"**Automatic Caching**: Once loaded