":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**Client-Side Hydration**: The sprite sheet is generated and injected after hydration, causing a brief paint event"},"324":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-104","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**DOM Output:**"},"325":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-105","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**Performance Benefits:**"},"326":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-106","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**Reduced DOM Size**: Path data stored once instead of duplicated"},"327":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-107","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**Lower Memory Usage**: Especially beneficial with many repeated icons"},"328":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-108","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**Faster Rendering**: Browser optimizations for `<use>` elements"},"329":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-109","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**Trade-offs:**"},"330":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-110","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**SSR Limitation**: Sprite references render empty until client-side hydration"},"331":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-111","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**Initial Flash**: Brief moment where icons appear/disappear during sprite injection"},"332":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-112","page_id":"/docs